ActNunavut Act
SubjectNunavut Court of Justice - Deputy Judges (a) Hon. John D. Rooke (b) Hon. Peter MacDonell Clark (c) Hon. W. Vaughan Hembroff (d) Hon. Brian C. Midwinter Beverley A. Browne
PrecisOrder appointing the Honourable: (a) John D. Rooke, (b) Peter MacDonell Clark, (c) W. Vaughan Hembroff, and (d) Brian C. Midwinter as Deputy Judges of the Nunavut Court of Justice to hold office during good behaviour until attaining the age of seventy-five years.
